Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主君 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是大地人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會發光的…翅膀
