Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涉谷的玩家村落變成了副本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 常蛾的巢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在涉谷的放送局遺址
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡變成了Raid區域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\b1\pos(776,670)}Zone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的名字叫呼聲迴響的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:23.89,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\an2\b1\fs30\pos(291,88)}呼聲迴響的要塞
